    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, add the <strong>asparagus tips</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5-6 min or until bright green and tender with a bite – these are your<strong> roasted asparagus tips</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
