    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>asparagus & chicken risotto</strong> topped with the <strong>roasted asparagus tips </strong>and a handful of <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with some <strong>olive oil</strong> and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
